source.name: * Measure 34 : Percentage of People Who Received Preventive Dental Services | Medicare Coverage
source.description: In order to define coverage types, disability is defined as follows: Individuals were identified as having a disability if any of the following conditions existed:  One or more Activities of Daily Living impairments, blindness, or deafness.
